  "Description": {
    "English": "An upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid, the Liquidator is a cutting-edge heavy-duty combat unit, designed to operate in the harshest of environments.<br><br>This limb override also functions as its own <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dedicated combat system</span>. It deploys high-velocity <span class=\"name name-technology\">stun projectiles</span>, perfect for keeping hostiles in place while advancing to close range.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "作为<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇的升级版本，清算员是一种尖端的重装作战单元，并且被设计成能够在最险恶的环境中执行任务。<br><br>这种肢体的超控系统也能够作为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">专用战斗系统</span>。它可以部署高速<span class=\"name name-technology\">眩晕弹</span>，这种弹药能够限制敌对目标行动并允许机体迅速接近敌人。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "清算人是一種尖端耐用戰鬥機體，為<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇的升級，專為在最嚴苛的環境中運作而設計。<br><br>此肢體覆寫能夠充當<span class=\"name name-stellar\">專用戰鬥系統</span>。會部署高速的<span class=\"name name-technology\">暈眩射彈</span>，是彌諾陶洛斯主砲的絕佳輔助武器，非常適合在迫近距離時，將敵對者凍結在原地。"
  },
